      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at pictures of deep space and then thinking about how everything just... ends. like the heat death of the universe. it makes everything we do feel so incredibly stupid. why even bother trying to build anything or be anything when it's all just going to be cold and empty anyway? it feels like we're just playing pretend in the dark.",
