    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"meaningful to us\" is just a cope. it doesn't change the fact that the suffering is real and the end is certain. if we know the outcome is just total nothingness, isn't it actually more rational to just stop the struggle now? to just opt out of the cycle before it drains everything from you? it seems more logical to find peace in the nothingness rather than fighting a losing battle for a temporary feeling.",
